milestones.description: Ryan Watson's 123 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for SCOT), surpassing Ryan Watson's 80
John Davison and Ashish Bagai's 89-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 66 between Chumney and Abdool Samad
Chumney and Qaiser Ali's 65-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 64 between Ashish Bagai and Sandeep Jyoti
Fraser Watts and Poonia's 47-run partnership is SCOT's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 20 between Neil MacRae and Poonia
Ryan Watson and Poonia's 99-run partnership is SCOT's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 29 between Ryan Watson and Poonia
Poonia has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (56) in an innings in ODIs for SCOT, going past Ryan Watson's 54
John Davison has broken the record for most ODIs (7) as captain for CAN, going past Joe Harris
Craig Wright has broken the record for most ODIs (6) as captain for SCOT, going past Salmond
